flowchart LR
    Users[Users / triggers] --> LB[Nginx / load balancer]
    LB --> W1[Worker replica 1]
    LB --> W2[Worker replica 2]
    LB --> WN[Worker replica N]
    W1 --> RDS[(AWS RDB/RDS<br/>durable platform state)]
    W2 --> RDS
    WN --> RDS
    W1 --> Redis[Redis<br/>cache, locks, sessions]
    W2 --> Redis
    WN --> Redis
    W1 --> Queue[Kafka / queue path<br/>long-running or high-volume work]
    W2 --> Queue
    Queue --> Exec[Distributed execution workers]
    Exec --> Providers[External providers]
    Exec --> RDS
    HPA[Kubernetes HPA<br/>scale on load] --> WN
